product_details:
The best phone camera; Take photos and videos so amazing, you won’t believe you actually took them. Capture small details, create perfect group shots, and even get vivid ones at night.

The dependable all-day battery The Adaptive Battery on Pixel 9a can last over 30 hours. Need even more? Turn on Extreme Battery Saver to make it last up to 100. That’s big energy.

One ask, done across your apps Save time by asking Gemini to find information and get things done for you across your Google apps – like Maps, Calendar, Gmail, and YouTube Music. It’s multitasking made easy.

It’s built to last Pixel 9a is designed to handle spills, dust, drops, and dings. From IP68 water and dust protection to a scratch-resistant display and long-lasting materials, it’s the most durable Pixel A-Series phone yet.

Talk things out live Instead of typing, use Gemini Live and have a natural, free-flowing conversation. Gemini follows along, even if you change the topic or switch the question mid-sentence.

Take the picture. And be in it, too Add Me makes sure no one is left out of a photo. Take one with the group, then swap in the photographer, and Pixel magically merges both photos.

Tiny is epic Use Macro Focus to reveal vivid color and striking contrast in photos and videos of the smallest details – like raindrops, flowers, or sprinkles.

product_name: easyfone Star - Safety Device Cum Phone for Kids with SOS, GPS Tracking, Discreet Listening, Photo Dial, No Internet, 10 Days Battery Backup, Parental Control by Seniorworld
product_details:
No number keypad – outgoing calls can only be made to pre-set numbers(max 20). Option to restrict incoming calls to pre-defined 20 numbers so that there is no chance of talking to strangers.

GPS to track location whenever you want. The easyfone star comes with a GPS that allows you to get your child’s location whenever you want or when your child triggers the emergency help button.

Dedicated SOS button ensures quick help in emergencies. Once triggered, the device automatically sends help messages (with the GPS location) and calls 5 emergency contacts repeatedly (upto 3 times) till someone answers – thereby saving precious time

No internet access, makes it an ideal choice for maintaining safety while staying connected with family. Parents can set up a “Do Not Disturb” time zone during which the phone operates in silent mode ensuring that there is no disturbance during sleep or study time.

Tamper-proof settings ensure the device can only be configured via the CareTouch App (Android) or website, giving you peace of mind that no one can alter the phone's settings.

Discreet Listening - Lets you listen discreetly to what is happening in your child’s surroundings. Useful when you want to make sure that your child is being looked after properly in your absence by an attendant.

Auto Call Back - Worried your child isn’t answering? Use the Auto Call Back feature by sending a command from an authorized phone, and the easyfone Star will call you with loudspeaker on.

Dock Charger - offers hassle-free charging, keeping the phone securely in place. It's safe for kids and ensures the device is always charged and ready to use.
